ChangeLog for densli
====================

1.0.3 (05-09-2012)
------------------

 - Allow spaces in -t/--timeago format for greater flexibility.
 - Fix handling of metrics API endpoint response format for some values that use lots of subkeys, when generating sparkblock graphs.

1.0.2 (31-08-2012)
------------------

 - Fix for errors being obfuscated if you use the -s/--spark option with metrics.getRange (gh issue #1).
 - Added -t/--timeago option to define a date range for metrics.getRange using a relative offset.

1.0.1 (31-08-2012)
------------------

 - Added -P/--postback option to send stdin as a raw JSON payload for use with the metrics.postback API endpoint.
 - Seperated sparks module to it's own python package (py-sparkblocks).

1.0.0 (30-08-2012)
------------------

 - Initial release for pypi.
